      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">15%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Sales increase</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">8 hrs</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Weekly time saved</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">92%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Fewer customer complaints</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="client-quote">
      <p>"I used to dread opening my laptop. Now I check my dashboard once in the morning, and everything just... works. I'm actually enjoying my business again."</p>
      <cite>- Sarah, Owner</cite>
    </div>

    <h2>
      <svg class="inline-block w-6 h-6 mr-2 text-coral" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
      </svg>
      The Common Thread
    </h2>

    <p>
      Three different industries. Three different challenges. But notice the pattern:
    </p>

